{"tid":2504173,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣中心吊頸 x 燒炭「雙凶宅」, 上層零議價500萬, 呎價14,124元","createTime":"2021-04-25T16:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T05:22:08.000Z","uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d220ca19b8433fba4b3e72b1773cac5487e72eac","tid":2504173,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"荃灣中心「雙凶宅」上一層兩房零議價500萬沽<br />\n上車屋苑之一的荃灣中心，1座一個兩房單位位處「雙凶宅」上一層，業主以「零議價」500萬元售出。樓齡已達40年的荃灣中心，美聯物業鍾家豪表示，屋苑1座高層F室，實用面積354方呎，建築面積455方呎，業主叫價500萬元，最終零議價沽出，實用呎價14,124元。原業主2015年8月斥資399.8萬元買入，帳面賺100萬元，升25%。<br />\n<br />\n成交單位樓下一層B室，據市場知悉，為兩度發生命案的凶宅，2002年先有租客於單位吊頸，其後2008年單位內有人燒炭，市場稱為「雙凶宅」，惟單位於匯豐銀行網上估價亦能得出估價506萬元，是否能估足價，則以銀行最終實際估價為準。至於，位處凶宅樓上一層亦不乏買家入市，市場相信是購買力追逐細價價，因而出現有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210425/RLML5VSUWRAMZOTINSSRYROU44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210425%2FRLML5VSUWRAMZOTINSSRYROU44%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=e7305e9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210425%2FRLML5VSUWRAMZOTINSSRYROU44%2F&h=20e01c84\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210425/RLML5VSUWRAMZOTINSSRYROU44/</a>"},{"pid":"0b24f874b7bc8f09cc83d22449da4228b9dee3b7","tid":2504173,"uid":187741,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"買凶宅呢啲好睇條命硬唔硬<br />\n一般人話算買得起，都未必受得起"},{"pid":"dacfa15ecdd6a66967cf998a6d48357c6902ebe5","tid":2504173,"uid":241949,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"上層都要驚咁上下左右前後左右都要驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8080cab96837a552dad55c03c9a778e4e937e182","tid":2504173,"uid":1652,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dacfa15ecdd6a66967cf998a6d48357c6902ebe5","tid":2504173,"uid":241949,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T16:06:40